name: Moraya Packaging
overview:
Incorporated in the year 2012, at Pune (Maharashtra, India), we, “Moraya Packaging India Private Limited,” are the leading name engaged in manufacturing and supplying a comprehensive assortment of Corrugated Box, Export Quality Heavy Duty Corrugated Boxes, Corrugated Roll and Corrugated Sheet, etc. Further, our offered range includes Sheet Rolls, Corrugated Sheets, Corrugated Box, etc.

Our Team: Designers Quality controllers Packaging Experts Sales & marketing executives Administrative staff

Our Quality Assurance: Consistently delivering superior quality products and remaining at the top requires major focus on quality and for maintaining it, we deliver our range of products that are manufactured using optimum grade wood and other raw material by employing the latest technologies.

Client Satisfaction: We have always been connected with experienced professionals since our inception, that’s why we have a pool of professionals which possess outstanding industry knowledge. The professionals appointed by us are well aware of the latest market trends of packaging industry.

Why Us?: We have positioned ourselves as a premier organization involves in fabricating qualitative products. Our crystal clear policies in business dealings, ethical trade practices and wide distribution network have enabled us to gain an edge over our industry counterparts.

Our Product Range: Corrugated Sheets Corrugated Boxes Bopp Tapes Corrugated Boxes With Handles Corrugated Boxes With Partitions Corrugates Boxes With Lids Custom Corrugated Boxes
